Program_Policies: A grade of C or better is required for all courses in the minor, as specified by Senate Policy 59-10. In addition, at least six credits of the minor must be unique from the prescribed courses required by a student's major(s).; BIOL 400, BIOL 496, and SC 495 credits may not be used to fulfill this requirement.
